tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE DanceCompetitors (
    competitor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    competitor_name VARCHAR(50),
    dance_style VARCHAR(50),
    score DECIMAL,
    event_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE Competition (
    competition_id UUID,
    competition_name VARCHAR(255),
    competition_date DATE,
    PRIMARY KEY (competition_id)
);
CREATE TABLE Dancer (
    dancer_id UUID,
    dancer_name VARCHAR(255),
    dancer_style VARCHAR(50),
    PRIMARY KEY (dancer_id)
);
CREATE TABLE Judge (
    judge_id UUID,
    judge_name VARCHAR(255),
    judge_expertise VARCHAR(100),
    PRIMARY KEY (judge_id)
);
CREATE TABLE Score (
    score_id UUID,
    competition_id UUID,
    dancer_id UUID,
    judge_id UUID,
    score DECIMAL(10,2),
    PRIMARY KEY (score_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (competition_id) REFERENCES Competition(competition_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (dancer_id) REFERENCES Dancer(dancer_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (judge_id) REFERENCES Judge(judge_id)
);
